<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<title>ThaiMart — PM Case-Study Prototypes</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Noto+Sans+Thai:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root{
    --primary:#E84A27; --primary-dark:#C13A1C; --green:#138A5E; --gold:#E8A33D;
    --ink:#1A1614; --muted:#6B6460; --surface:#fff; --canvas:#F7F3EF; --hair:#E9E1D8;
    --r:14px; --shadow:0 1px 3px rgba(26,22,20,.08),0 8px 24px rgba(26,22,20,.06);
  }
  *{box-sizing:border-box}
  body{margin:0;font-family:Inter,'Noto Sans Thai',system-ui,sans-serif;color:var(--ink);
    background:var(--canvas);line-height:1.5;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased}
  .wrap{max-width:1080px;margin:0 auto;padding:48px 24px 72px}
  header{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:8px}
  .logo{width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:12px;background:var(--primary);color:#fff;
    display:grid;place-items:center;font-weight:700;font-size:20px;box-shadow:var(--shadow)}
  h1{font-size:15px;font-weight:600;margin:0;letter-spacing:.2px}
  .lede{font-size:34px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-.5px;margin:28px 0 10px;max-width:18ch}
  .sub{font-size:17px;color:var(--muted);max-width:60ch;margin:0 0 36px}
  .grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(300px,1fr));gap:20px}
  a.card{display:flex;flex-direction:column;text-decoration:none;color:inherit;background:var(--surface);
    border:1px solid var(--hair);border-radius:var(--r);padding:24px;box-shadow:var(--shadow);
    transition:transform .15s ease,box-shadow .15s ease}
  a.card:hover{transform:translateY(-3px);box-shadow:0 6px 14px rgba(26,22,20,.12),0 18px 40px rgba(26,22,20,.10)}
  a.card:focus-visible{outline:2px solid var(--primary);outline-offset:3px}
  .tag{display:inline-flex;align-self:flex-start;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;padding:5px 11px;
    border-radius:999px;margin-bottom:14px}
  .t1{background:#FCE9E2;color:var(--primary-dark)}
  .t2{background:#E2F1EA;color:var(--green)}
  .t3{background:#FBF0DC;color:#9A6A18}
  .card h2{font-size:20px;margin:0 0 4px;font-weight:700}
  .card .concept{font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);margin:0 0 14px}
  .card p{font-size:14px;color:var(--ink);margin:0 0 18px;flex:1}
  .kpi{display:flex;gap:18px;border-top:1px solid var(--hair);padding-top:14px;margin-bottom:16px}
  .kpi div{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted)}
  .kpi b{display:block;font-size:18px;color:var(--ink);font-weight:700}
  .open{font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:var(--primary);display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px}
  footer{margin-top:44px;font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);border-top:1px solid var(--hair);padding-top:20px}
  footer b{color:var(--ink)}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrap">
  <header>
    <div class="logo">T</div>
    <h1>ThaiMart · Product Prototypes</h1>
  </header>

  <p class="lede">Three product bets, three working prototypes.</p>
  <p class="sub">PM case-study artifacts for ThaiMart. Each is a self-contained, clickable hi-fi prototype with a
    “How it works” view covering the problem, persona, target KPIs, and a system / service-blueprint diagram —
    showing how a business requirement gets technicalized.</p>

  <div class="grid">
    <a class="card" href="01-smartrewards.html">
      <span class="tag t1">Personalization · Retention</span>
      <h2>SmartRewards &amp; Predictive Cart</h2>
      <p class="concept">AI loyalty + recommendation widget in the ThaiMart app</p>
      <p>Bargain Hunter vs Convenience Shopper personas drive personalized recs — to cut churn without eroding margin on blanket discounts.</p>
      <div class="kpi">
        <div>Repeat purchase<b>+15%</b></div>
        <div>AOV<b>+10%</b></div>
      </div>
      <span class="open">Open prototype →</span>
    </a>

    <a class="card" href="02-localpick.html">
      <span class="tag t2">Operations · Fulfillment</span>
      <h2>LocalPick</h2>
      <p class="concept">Real-time store stock + 2-hour curbside pickup</p>
      <p>Shopper reserves in-store stock; staff app picks &amp; stages. Service blueprint maps both journeys. MVP scoped to one pilot store.</p>
      <div class="kpi">
        <div>Fulfilment SLA<b>&lt; 2 hrs</b></div>
        <div>Pilot<b>1 store</b></div>
      </div>
      <span class="open">Open prototype →</span>
    </a>

    <a class="card" href="03-vendorexpress.html">
      <span class="tag t3">B2B · Marketplace Platform</span>
      <h2>VendorExpress</h2>
      <p class="concept">Self-service vendor onboarding + catalog dashboard</p>
      <p>Automated KYC, bulk catalog upload, and AI auto-categorization replace 14 days of manual ops data entry.</p>
      <div class="kpi">
        <div>Onboarding<b>14d → 48h</b></div>
        <div>Entry<b>Self-serve</b></div>
      </div>
      <span class="open">Open prototype →</span>
    </a>
  </div>

  <footer>
    <b>How to demo:</b> open any prototype, use the top tab to switch between the clickable <b>Prototype</b> flow and
    the <b>How it works</b> view (diagrams + PM reasoning). Async actions are faked with short timers; screen and form
    state persist across reloads.
  </footer>
</div>
</body>
</html>
